<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.1.5">
<l>paṇimiṉ ṟiruvaru ḷeṉṉumañcītap paimpūmpaḷḷi</l>
<l>aṇimeṉ kuḻalā riṉpakkalavi yamutuṇṭār</l>
<l>tuṇimuṉpu nālappal lēḻaiyar tāmiḻip paccelvar</l>
<l>maṇimiṉṉu mēṉinam māyavaṉ pērcolli vāḻmiṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Be humble! Those who eat ambrosia uniting in pleasure with [women with] ornate,</l>
<l>soft curls on pretty, cool, fresh, flower beds who speak about holy graces/favours</l>
<l>they will go while a piece [of cloth] hangs in front, while many fools degrade [them].</l>
<l>Live speaking the names of our Dark one with a sapphire-flashing body.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
